<script type="text/javascript">
      //<![CDATA[
      function removeHtmlTag(strx,chop){ 
        if(strx.indexOf("<")!=-1)
        {
          var s = strx.split("<"); 
          for(var i=0;i<s.length;i++){ 
            if(s[i].indexOf(">")!=-1){ 
              s[i] = s[i].substring(s[i].indexOf(">")+1,s[i].length); 
            } 
          } 
          strx =  s.join(""); 
        }
        chop = (chop < strx.length-1) ? chop : strx.length-2; 
        while(strx.charAt(chop-1)!=' ' && strx.indexOf(' ',chop)!=-1) chop++; 
        strx = strx.substring(0,chop-1); 
        return strx+'...'; 
      }
      function createSummaryAndThumb(pID){
        var div = document.getElementById(pID);
        var imgtag = "";
        var img = div.getElementsByTagName("img");
        var summ = summary_noimg;
        if(img.length>=1) {	
          imgtag = '<span style="float:right; padding:0px 0px 5px 10px;"><img src="'+img[0].src+'" width="'+img_thumb_width+'px" height="'+img_thumb_height+'px"/></span>';
          summ = summary_img;
        }
        var summary = imgtag + '<div>' + removeHtmlTag(div.innerHTML,summ) + '</div>';
        div.innerHTML = summary;
      }
      //]]>
</script>

<div class="post-body entry-content">
<p>
</p><div dir="rtl" style="text-align: right;" trbidi="on">
<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
<a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-_HQouHGc3pI/VOB2gyhCujI/AAAAAAAABH8/3unN1_ywUss/s1600/1pNkP9O.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-_HQouHGc3pI/VOB2gyhCujI/AAAAAAAABH8/3unN1_ywUss/s1600/1pNkP9O.jpg" height="356" width="640"></a></div>
<span style="font-size: large;">فقرة الألعاب الأسبوعية : تحميل لعبة الأكشن الرائعة والخفيفة AssaultCube + اللعب أون لاين</span><br>
<span style="font-size: large;">في إطار الفقرة الأسبوعية للألعاب التي نخصصها كل سبت للتعريف ببعض الألعاب المجانية والخفيفة على الجهاز، نلتقي في هذه الفقرة مع لعبة الأكشن </span><span style="color: blue; font-size: x-large;"><a href="http://adf.ly/12HyNA" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">AssaultCube </a></span><span style="font-size: large;"><span style="color: blue;"><a href="http://adf.ly/12HyNA" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Reloaded</a></span> الرائعة جدا والتي لا يتجاوز حجمها 47 mb ، تستطيع اللعب أون لاين عبرسرفرات متنوعة ، فبعد تثبيتك للعبة والدخول إليها تضغط على مفتاح esc في الكيبورد ثم تختار <span style="color: blue;"><a href="http://adf.ly/12HyNA" target="_blank">multiplayer</a></span> للدخول إلى السيرفوات المتوفرة</span><br>
<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
<a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-iaTh4ZlscsQ/VOB3owmwUZI/AAAAAAAABIM/BGTyTbvsppU/s1600/Enemy-Strike.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-iaTh4ZlscsQ/VOB3owmwUZI/AAAAAAAABIM/BGTyTbvsppU/s1600/Enemy-Strike.jpg" height="400" width="640"></a><span style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: #0000ee;"><u><span style="font-size: large;">Paragraph weekly games: Download game and brilliant light Action AssaultCube + Play Online Under paragraph weekly for games that N_khassa every Saturday for the definition of some of the free and light gaming on the device, we meet in this paragraph with Game Action AssaultCube Reloaded very brilliant and which does not exceed the size of 47 mb, you can play online Abrserfrat variety, after installing the game and access to press the key esc on the keyboard and then choose to enter the multiplayer Alserfouat available - </span>See more at:&nbsp;</u></span></span></div>
<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
<a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-y_5dNcJLQn0/VOB4PvhQr_I/AAAAAAAABIU/MxGApmTzZ7w/s1600/20131014_000730_ac_gothic_teamdeathmatch-Copy_zps21c2769e.png" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-y_5dNcJLQn0/VOB4PvhQr_I/AAAAAAAABIU/MxGApmTzZ7w/s1600/20131014_000730_ac_gothic_teamdeathmatch-Copy_zps21c2769e.png" height="480" width="640"></a></div>
<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
<a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-6JlKnrW-CcY/VOB5gclgAtI/AAAAAAAABIg/6Ok4awnFgw0/s1600/images.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-6JlKnrW-CcY/VOB5gclgAtI/AAAAAAAABIg/6Ok4awnFgw0/s1600/images.jpg" height="400" width="400"></a></div>
<div>
<h2 style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding-top: 10px; text-align: center;">
<span style="color: blue; font-size: x-large;"><i><u><a href="http://adf.ly/12IfJb" target="_blank">AssaultCube</a></u></i></span></h2>
</div>
<div>

Mohamed Alawadly
